ne biosynthesis II (fungi) () (PWY-7550) = GO:0140479\\n\\nSo, these could be added as exactMatch xrefs to the two child terms.\\n\\nHowever, these specific variant pathways are really beyond scope of GO (they can be represented as GO-CAMs if necessary) so it would be better to obsolete the two child terms (replaced by the GO:0052699 parent term) and add the two MetaCyc xrefs as narrowMatch to GO:0052699. \\n\\n(This was noted previously in https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/11163)\",\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
